r side.\u00a0</li>\r\n<li>You can install a Siddha Shukra Tantra to get rid of all the negative energy in the room.\u00a0</li>\r\n<li>Use a Siddha Vastu Kalash to boost the positive energy which can be generated from the corner of the house.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Plan for an East-Facing Vastu House\u00a0</strong></p>\r\n<p>For those constructing an east-facing home, it is pertinent to adhere to Vastu Shastra to facilitate positive energy. While many interior designers and architects follow basic Vastu, for those who want in-depth compliance with the science, Vastu Shastra experts can also be consulted. The following table demonstrates in what direction your east-facing home should be designed as per Vastu stated norms.\u00a0</p>\r\n<table width=\"609\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p><strong>S. No. </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p><strong>Type of Room</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p><strong>Preferred direction as per Vastu Shastra</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p>1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p>Guest room, kitchen, living room</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p>North-West</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p>2</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p>Drawing room, living room, office</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p>North</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p>3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p>Pooja Room</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p>North-East</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p>4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p>Study room, dining room, children&#8217;s room</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p>West</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<p>5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"269\">\r\n<p>Verandah, atrium, entrance lobby, balconies and other open spaces</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"265\">\r\n<p>East</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"75\">\r\n<