ositions and offices along with businessmen or businesswomen. Musicians, artists and other creative professionals like dancers will also benefit. When doing up an east-facing room, make sure that it gets ample natural light every morning and use artificial light later on in the day as well. Choose colors like green and blue in this case. Blue and light grey tint make for an excellent combination along with aqua and light green hues alike. Neutral tones such as light pink and white are great options as well.\r\nThese are some aspects that you should always keep in mind while planning or building your east facing house. The Vastu tips will help you embrace better living while avoiding several issues along the journey as well. You will get several plans which are readily available online for your perusal.\r\nFAQs\r\n\r\n What are the recommended wall paint colours for east-facing rooms?\u00a0\r\n\r\nAfter visualizing the room in natural as well as artificial light, the ideal colours for such rooms are different shades of blue, green, grey, and aqua.\u00a0\r\n\r\n What type of plants are considered lucky for east-facing houses?\u00a0\r\n\r\nLucky\u00a0plants for east-facing homes\u00a0are aloe vera, daffodils, citrus plants, money plants, neem plants, basil plants, lucky bamboo, a banana plant, and plum blossoms to name a few.\u00a0\r\n\r\n Is an east-facing house the best option as per Vastu compliance?\u00a0\r\n\r\nAfter north-facing houses, east-facing houses are the second-best option for Vastu compliant homes.\u00a0\r\n\r\n Can lack Vastu Shastra cause disruptions to personal lives?\u00a0\r\n\r\nVastu Shastra is a study of layout, design, ventilation, and mainly directions of a property. It is a practical approach to avoid destruction, disturbances and overall aids in creating a spacious and free-flowing atmosphere. Naturally, when the harmony of this is affected, it can cause disruptions in the personal lives of those living there.\u00a0\r\n\r\n In case there is n